<h2>4. Bruce Boyer Books (True Style / Elegance)</h2>

<p>First, let me say I&rsquo;m a great admirer of Bruce and of all the authors I mentioned here, I think he has the best writing style. On top of that, he has a wonderful personal style. So why didn&rsquo;t it make my list?</p>

